{"type":"message","id":"1bd34538","parentId":"8bcc19e5","timestamp":"2026-03-30T00:01:07.633Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_1UTpf8MNhUAvPFwZhVuOiDC5|fc_093e06e7855dd07a0169c9bd46028c81918e4b3cece626b2f5","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"body\": \"---------- Forwarded message ---------\\r\\nDe: Andrea Martínez <amartinez@zoolatech.com>\\r\\nDate: mar, 24 mar 2026 a las 14:52\\r\\nSubject: Zoolatech coding challenge\\r\\nTo: <toledo970501@gmail.com>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\nHello Gustavo!\\r\\nHere you can find the coding challenge.\\r\\nYou will answer it and send me once you finish, you can take 1-2 days to\\r\\ncomplete it. The task typically takes 1-2 hours to complete.\\r\\n\\r\\nThe coding challenge is attached to this email\\r\\nPlease let me know if you have any questions\\r\\nGreetings\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\nAndrea Martínez\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n-- \\r\\n*Gustavo Adolfo Toledo Barandica*\\r\\n🧑🏾💻 Cloud & Software Solutions Architect | Electronics Engineer\\r\\n------------------------------\\r\\n📞 +57 318 371 8246 <+573183718246> | 📧 toledo970501@gmail.com\\r\\n📍 Colombia\\r\\n------------------------------\\r\\n[image: LinkedIn]LinkedIn\\r\\n<https://www.linkedin.com/in/gustavotoledo97/>[image:\\r\\nGitHub]GitHub <https://github.com/GustavoToledo97>\\r\\n\",\n  \"headers\": {\n    \"bcc\": \"\",\n    \"cc\": \"\",\n    \"date\": \"Wed, 25 Mar 2026 20:31:57 -0500\",\n    \"from\": \"Gustavo Toledo <toledo970501@gmail.com>\",\n    \"subject\": \"Fwd: Zoolatech coding challenge\",\n    \"to\": \"atlas.ia.agente@gmail.com\"\n  }\n}"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":742,"aggregated":"{\n  \"body\": \"---------- Forwarded message ---------\\r\\nDe: Andrea Martínez <amartinez@zoolatech.com>\\r\\nDate: mar, 24 mar 2026 a las 14:52\\r\\nSubject: Zoolatech coding challenge\\r\\nTo: <toledo970501@gmail.com>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\nHello Gustavo!\\r\\nHere you can find the coding challenge.\\r\\nYou will answer it and send