{"type":"message","id":"94b55612","parentId":"6411680a","timestamp":"2026-03-30T00:01:31.708Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"**Planning tomorrow's events**\n\nI need to create two events for tomorrow: one at 9 am for reviewing and rotating exposed secrets, and another at 10 am for following up on the Zoolatech challenge. Since the challenge is overdue, I wonder if I should mention that instead of focusing on scheduling. I’ll schedule task blocks and invite attendees via email. It makes sense to create concise calendar tasks with clear summaries and descriptions. I'll use the primary Atlas calendar for this.","thinkingSignature":"{\"id\":\"rs_093e06e7855dd07a0169c9bd541a588191b18b703613c0ad6f\",\"type\":\"reasoning\",\"encrypted_content\":\"gAAAAABpyb1YAIaetPxjgWavMgGAhBcDSGKfWpUVCwq04Tn1KmMZoTMcqxYvLf2dwLkkC1y4n8w5-7rAhOq2ZaxIEPMc-B-fjbT0AqLDKTqtOlA8-vubBu7VHGOA4MisoxbKKe4Zx5I_03R2KnNL-DV_UoDXiENWgUAuWn5bTcTTI8zlWUaaUiOrw14gzP4cX-RfEFApe8gKGVskkOnufXOLgOhVH395GMDfXDJTvI1CgUPMgvlh64Yl4_WGP1bFz_QgPhnSSLieLdikmJx85eq9436pvWvzC3qJM0pX_En6S6FVW-5L1brRsSfa9Fi7hYvPNkMOVIbyZqpWPc-ymho1Pw4wYt9g_zWdnHqBQIJ4VSkyRCf0QfC2p6CtlctxrKWchEvm1TvOcQm1O-2LJILAqTciphPD8tAaHOu2_-l1MT-UXsrln6ZrGRV_RMldMBcbwg4fWGhAfbG34w4LmLD8yKWElVT34uWvK1kBeBpfq0Pc5L3H2vrJpRZmQnIag-xoRmsw3UGCoRuLjdrv0f_vf70PwXsqP482t58khF6zfuVEKLZGp5yPqNtgTqkNJuSMJ1VSUdQupEF4Hsv1gBLk07carMsdSQ1tq098voxtvyCDcnKfj61zXGkEjh8e3GnhxaLfA4DW2j1na2vzX9ro6jReYuaB8EJraWJtTfWR3BV86pWMIhnnAWYBBMGv1g_49sP1g-eVGKYSTjXbZHhLBKUFHSdfruz2d35xaLxfV61mwivT1sPP1I8AjRUjE_gvA2sNtKItyBLBYZHfnUXONbJaUJVhiIfY5vrlNAeXln2KnIMf4Bt2vbr6iz9sdD8eD3XIrOnqi2lxvtBVZsuNCtUvVKaP3aSJznKFT2nEehBpjhoH9uFtt7w1kYSdQRHxjizvi3b3kD-NQDQJAUxNy43vVFkg8y-DrkaT9z4Ph5_4Kzb12BWawPEdcLAyh1V3ddPoI2e1XWxAkZjGmj_E-yWdNQF5W6Hfwoz_l1De-Y6E2wXCOj0andBET0-ig7N5sbf_4dpf8oDGmy97SwhQAq-2x1C06lPu4Y6Kbxx5DVS4ijYGUFU3UeDA9MPtPmqHchtxgoUSP12xV9W8CBBGxOTyRX-_If7gEnpzCI92uXrXsrRPgavU_ZGaipac8MQMBo2BysA1f4FVoscYLPSLxluxM-IJf_AM8hLIRxc_TJJ3kKqtC0bfchAajrkM95GLbDdnB1BeJFrHWTXVB2xiHU2GtGQ7pUbG0aEjrM-2i4sOrRhxNPygl_7hSQaKwzr4Xt53UYrir_n1BaDc0KFYFSjnrCCIL5Ni7_hU2eihq0yBcRd-WiATg3KDNLhFS8shqKsY8fSU3DJhs0pWHr0z3xChdheJbzCG7CWzTlkmOh4eYMAjCJXMo5-P3CDLF79km9MLzsuPnMkidgloK1U147ANz335mApkYKbi8UyUD1rJuCc1cWEYg5rppOlG9xmahWxEI4Mo7zancAPg6j3udL-khisY4g==\",\"summary\":[{\"type\":\"summary_text\",\"text\":\"**Planning tomorrow's events**\\n\\nI need to create two events for tomorrow: one at 9 am for reviewing and rotating exposed secrets, and another at 10 am for following up on the Zoolatech challenge. Since the challenge is overdue, I wonder if I should mention that instead of focusing on scheduling. I’ll schedule task blocks and invite attendees via email. It makes sense to create concise calendar tasks with clear summaries and descriptions. I'll use the primary Atlas calendar for this.\"}]}"},{"type":"text","text":"Voy a dejar dos bloques para mañana en el calendario de Atlas, compartidos con Gustavo, porque son lo único realmente urgente que salió del inbox: el leak de secretos y el challenge de Zoolatech ya vencido.","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_093e06e7855dd07a0169c9bd5834b48191bdc19f56b251a500\",\"phase\":\"commentary\"}"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_iHpM9TyEQIXo3KAt54Pd8An9|fc_093e06e7855dd07a0169c9bd584b3881918e30efd7ea40c223","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"$env:GOG_ACCOUNT='atlas.ia.agente@gmail.com';\n$desc1 = @'\nPendiente detectado en Gmail el 29 Mar 2026.\n\n- GitHub secret scanning + GitGuardian detectaron una Supabase Service Role JWT / Service Key expuesta en atlasiaagente-alt/openclaw-assistant\n- Ubicación reportada: agents/prometeo/sessions/923f7941-8832-4b11-baab-70573a106770.jsonl (commit 18920052)\n- Acción: rotar/revocar secreto, limpiar historial o archivo expuesto, cerrar alerta en GitHub/GitGuardian\n'@;\ngog calendar create atlas.ia.agente@gmail.com --summary \"URGENTE: revisar leak de secretos en GitHub/Supabase\" --from 2026-03-30T09:00:00-05:00 --to 2026-03-30T09:45:00-05:00 --description $desc1 --attendee toledo970501@gmail.com --event-color 11 --json --results-only --no-input;\n$desc2 = @'\nPendiente visto en Gmail.\n\n- Forward de Andrea Martínez (Zoolatech) enviado el 25 Mar\n- Challenge original recibido el 24 Mar con ventana estimada de entrega de 1-2 días\n- Acción: revisar si ya se entregó; si no, responder/renegociar o cerrar seguimiento\n'@;\ngog calendar create atlas.ia.agente@gmail.com --summary \"Seguimiento: Zoolatech coding challenge\" --from 2026-03-30T10:00:00-05:00 --to 2026-03-30T10:30:00-05:00 --description $desc2 --attendee toledo970501@gmail.com --event-color 5 --json --results-only --no-input","workdir":"C:\\Users\\Gustavo\\.openclaw\\workspace","yieldMs":10000,"timeout":60},"partialJson":"{\"command\":\"$env:GOG_ACCOUNT='atlas.ia.agente@gmail.com';\\n$desc1 = @'\\nPendiente detectado en Gmail el 29 Mar 2026.\\n\\n- GitHub secret scanning + GitGuardian detectaron una Supabase Service Role JWT / Service Key expuesta en atlasiaagente-alt/openclaw-assistant\\n- Ubicación reportada: agents/prometeo/sessions/923f7941-8832-4b11-baab-70573a106770.jsonl (commit 18920052)\\n- Acción: rotar/revocar secreto, limpiar historial o archivo expuesto, cerrar alerta en GitHub/GitGuardian\\n'@;\\ngog calendar create atlas.ia.agente@gmail.com --summary \\\"URGENTE: revisar leak de secretos en GitHub/Supabase\\\" --from 2026-03-30T09:00:00-05:00 --to 2026-03-30T09:45:00-05:00 --description $desc1 --attendee toledo970501@gmail.com --event-color 11 --json --results-only --no-input;\\n$desc2 = @'\\nPendiente visto en Gmail.\\n\\n- Forward de Andrea Martínez (Zoolatech) enviado el 25 Mar\\n- Challenge original recibido el 24 Mar con ventana estimada de entrega de 1-2 días\\n- Acción: revisar si ya se entregó; si no, responder/renegociar o cerrar seguimiento\\n'@;\\ngog calendar create atlas.ia.agente@gmail.com --summary \\\"Seguimiento: Zoolatech coding challenge\\\" --from 2026-03-30T10:00:00-05:00 --to 2026-03-30T10:30:00-05:00 --de